cetus.analysis

Interface Domain

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NullDomain, PointsToDomain, PointsToDomain.Universe, RangeDomain, SetDomain

    public interface Domain
    A class that implements Domain is used to represent container for data used in data flow analysis. The following methods are common to most of the data flow analysis.
